If you buy them in 10000s, you can get any frequency of crystal you want.<br />For our purposes, the answer is no, you cannot get a 6×NTSC CB crystal anymore.<br />You can still get: 1×, 4×, 8×, only. (You can get PAL CB ×1, ×4, and something very close to PAL CB×6; it's too fast by 1815ppm)<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3512">lidnariq</a> — Fri Jan 11, 2013 5:30 pm</p><hr />
